{"tid":1141609,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！唔洗鬥長命！「騎馬與砍殺II：領主」將首度公開試玩","createTime":"2019-05-06T14:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T19:50:37.000Z","uid":33359,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6e068f33627b85c2423b461938e3ea7550714e04","tid":1141609,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:49:23.000Z","msg":"人氣中世紀戰爭作《騎馬與砍殺II：領主》將首度公開試玩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/33288/Mount-Blade-II-Bannerlord\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F33288%2FMount-Blade-II-Bannerlord&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHr%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=c088ac81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/33288/Mount-Blade-II-Bannerlord</a><br />\n<br />\n由 TaleWorlds Entertainment 開發的中世 RPG 《騎馬與砍殺II：領主》(Mount &amp;<br />\nBlade II: Bannerlord) 首次公佈後已經有一段時間了，官方近日宣佈遊戲將會參展「<br />\ngamescom 2019」，並將首度公開試玩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5CCsFGt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5CCsFGt.jpg&h=9445ef85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《騎馬與砍殺II：領主》由 2012 年首度公開露面已經 7 年時間，遊戲依然在開發階段<br />\n，粉絲們都等到快放棄了，不過近日官方公佈有新消息。《騎馬與砍殺II：領主》將會<br />\n在 2019 年 8 月 21 日至 8 月 24 日於德國科隆科隆國際展覽會舉行的「gamescom<br />\n2019」上參展。<br />\n<br />\n届時會向玩家提供限時試玩，讓到場玩家先行體驗《騎馬與砍殺II：領主》的多人遊戲模<br />\n式和戰鬥系統等等內容。《騎馬與砍殺II：領主》暫時推出日期未定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dNMG0EK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdNMG0EK.jpg&h=91a3d218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xZrOAc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxZrOAc2.jpg&h=2e5b6411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eYQEB44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeYQEB44.jpg&h=f4b28b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDev Blog 02/05/19<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.taleworlds.com/en/Games/Bannerlord/Blog/108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taleworlds.com%2Fen%2FGames%2FBannerlord%2FBlog%2F108&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHr%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=e7847da2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.taleworlds.com/en/Games/Bannerlord/Blog/108</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Steam/M.1557123453.A.AC6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FSteam%2FM.1557123453.A.AC6.html&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHr%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=eef40640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Steam/M.1557123453.A.AC6.html</a>"},{"pid":"1ddcb7815aac9132bb28355420ad45c14e85e37b","tid":1141609,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5754b794cd46da77e07881f4f6fa93dfdc6df496","tid":1141609,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:00:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"518cc04cd2726f895c210760d46b916ddb3e476c","tid":1141609,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c23208f9159ab1d09cd8411d4acd5a650f67a8","tid":1141609,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:08:38.000Z","msg":"《騎馬與砍殺II：領主》暫時推出日期未定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51ab2b0560f820fc822e25320b547fc8037726e","tid":1141609,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"望到個大地圖即刻J咗"},{"pid":"e4f56ae69e69dd6fd820058f138e244bc03b9fed","tid":1141609,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87c23208f9159ab1d09cd8411d4acd5a650f67a8","tid":1141609,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:08:38.000Z","msg":"《騎馬與砍殺II：領主》暫時推出日期未定。<i